      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and sophisticated engineering. This automobile has been meticulously maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring a driving experience that remains consistent, refined, and dependable. Having passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, it stands as a testament to enduring quality and represents a superior acquisition for the discerning buyer seeking exceptional value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
