      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home! It\u2019s been super well-loved and is in great shape for its next adventure. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go and runs so smoothly. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how much fun it is to drive! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and can't wait to see this car go to a great owner!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a cross-bank exhaust manifold to achieve its signature 8,400 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry is enhanced by Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable damping rates for varying lateral load requirements. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis remains stiff, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the communicative feedback expected of this generation. A well-sorted example for the purist who values atmospheric induction and mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been maintained with a 'no-expense-spared' philosophy regarding its mechanical health. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use such as small stone chips on the front fascia. The body panels are straight, with consistent gaps and no evidence of past major repairs. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather seats are supple with minimal wear on the bolsters, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control, premium sound system, and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs smoothly, benefiting from a recent comprehensive service that included new filters and a fluid flush. The transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension remains tight, providing a comfortable yet responsive ride. This car has been a dependable companion and is ready for its next chapter with a new owner who appreciates a well-documented and honest vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its consistent maintenance history and refined mechanical integrity. This specimen offers an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value, having been curated to meet our exacting standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal. It represents a premier choice for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience without compromise.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for this reliable ride. It\u2019s been well-loved and is still in wonderful shape for all your upcoming adventures! It runs smoothly and is totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. I\u2019ve really enjoyed driving this one, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS for optimal volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates and the rod bearings have been replaced, addressing critical platform-specific maintenance. The suspension maintains its factory kinematics with refreshed bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and communicative feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. While the finish shows minor road patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain sharp.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
